### ðŸš¨ Error Cases and Edge Case Testing

### 404 Errors - Data Not Found

### Non-existent year - before available data
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/2010

### Non-existent year - way in the past
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/1995

### Future year beyond available data
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/2030

### 400 Errors - Invalid Input

### Year too old (before 1800)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/1799

### Year too far in future
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/2101

### Invalid year format
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/abc

### 422 Errors - Validation Errors

### Same start and end year for value change
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 2020,
  "end_year": 2020
}

### Negative amount for current value
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2020,
  "amount": -50.0
}

### Zero amount for current value
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2020,
  "amount": 0
}

### Invalid year range in value change request
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 1799,
  "end_year": 2020
}

### Future original year for current value
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2030
}

### Current year as original year
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2025
}

### Invalid JSON format
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2020,
  "amount": "not_a_number"
}

### Missing required fields
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 2020
}

### Edge Cases - Boundary Values

### Minimum valid year
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/1800

### Maximum valid year (current year)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/rate/2025

### Very small amount
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2020,
  "amount": 0.01
}

### Very large amount
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/current-value
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "original_year": 2020,
  "amount": 1000000.0
}